{"kanda":6,"sarga":97,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"तथातैःकृत्तगात्रैस्तुदशग्रीवेणमार्गणैः ।बभूववसुधातत्रप्रकीर्णाहरिभिस्तदा","trans":"That time the battlefield was strewn with bodies of Vanaras whose limbs had been severed by the arrows of Ravana.","words":[{"d":"दशग्रीवेण","m":"by Ravana"},{"d":"तथा","m":"that way"},{"d":"मार्गणैः","m":"on the way"},{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"कृत्तगात्रैः","m":"limbs severed"},{"d":"तैः","m":"those"},{"d":"हरिभिः","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"तत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"वसुधा","m":"on the ground"},{"d":"प्रकीर्णा","m":"strewn बभूव witnessed"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"रावणस्याप्रसह्यंतंशरसम्पातमेकतः ।न शेकुस्सहितुंदीप्तंपतङ्गाज्वलनंयथा","trans":"Just as moths cannot bear the blazing fire, the Vanaras could not bear the glowing hail of Ravana's arrows even for an instant.","words":[{"d":"एकतः","m":"for an instant"},{"d":"रावणस्य","m":"Ravana's"},{"d":"तम्","m":"them"},{"d":"शरसम्पातम्","m":"hail of arrows"},{"d":"दीप्तम्","m":"glowing"},{"d":"ज्वलनम्","m":"blazing"},{"d":"पतङ्गाःयथा","m":"like the moths"},{"d":"सहितुम्","m":"to bear"},{"d":"न शेकुः","m":"not possible"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"तेऽर्दितानिशितैर्बाणैःक्रोशन्तोविप्रदुद्रुवुः ।पावकार्चिस्समाविष्टादह्यमानायथागजाः","trans":"Tormented by sharp arrows, the scorched Vanaras fled screaming like elephants enveloped in flames.","words":[{"d":"बाणैः","m":"arrows"},{"d":"अर्दिताः","m":"tormented"},{"d":"ते","m":"they"},{"d":"पावकार्चिःसमाविष्टाः","m":"enveloped in flames"},{"d":"दह्यमानाः","m":"burning"},{"d":"गजाःयथा","m":"like the elephants"},{"d":"क्रोशन्तः","m":"scorched"},{"d":"विप्रदुद्रुवु","m":"fled screaming"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"प्लवङ्गनामनीकानिमहाभ्राणीवमारुतः ।सययौसमरेतस्मिन्विधमन्रावणश्शरैः","trans":"At that time, driven by Ravana's arrows, the Vanaras fled from the battlefield just like huge clouds are dissipated by wind.","words":[{"d":"तस्मिन्","m":"in that time"},{"d":"समरे","m":"in the battle"},{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana's"},{"d":"शरैः","m":"arrows"},{"d":"महाभ्राणि","m":"huge clouds"},{"d":"मारुतःइव","m":"like wind"},{"d":"प्लवङ्गमानाम्","m":"leaping"},{"d":"अनीकानि","m":"many"},{"d":"विधमन्","m":"dissipate"},{"d":"संययौ","m":"went in the battlefield"}]},{"v":5,"dev":"कदनंतरसाकृत्वाराक्षसेन्ध्रोवनौकसाम् ।आससादततोत्वरितंयुद्धेराघवंस्तदा","trans":"The Rakshasa king, having destroyed the forest rangers, thereafter, went to Raghava hurriedly.","words":[{"d":"राक्षसेन्द्रः","m":"Rakshasa king"},{"d":"युद्धे","m":"in war"},{"d":"वनौकसाम्","m":"forest rangers"},{"d":"कदनम्","m":"in the battlefield"},{"d":"तरसा","m":"hurriedly"},{"d":"कृत्वा","m":"went"},{"d":"ततः","m":"thereafter"},{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"त्वरितम्","m":"swiftly"},{"d":"राघवम्","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"आससाद","m":"approached"}]},{"v":6,"dev":"सुग्रीवस्तान्कपीन्दृष्टवाभग्नान्विद्रावितान्रणे ।गुल्मेसुषेणंनिक्षिप्यचक्रेयुद्धेऽद्भुतंमनः","trans":"Seeing the defeated and broken monkeys, Sugriva assigned Sushena for their protection and went to the battle making others wonder at his wonderful action.","words":[{"d":"भग्नान्","m":"broken"},{"d":"विद्रवतान्","m":"defeated"},{"d":"तान् कपीन्","m":"those monkeys"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"सुषेणम्","m":"Sushena"},{"d":"गुल्मे","m":"for protection"},{"d":"निक्षिप्य","m":"having assigned"},{"d":"अद्भुतम्","m":"wonderful"},{"d":"मनः","m":"mind"},{"d":"युद्धे","m":"to the battle"},{"d":"चक्रे","m":"went"}]},{"v":7,"dev":"आत्मनस्सदृशंवीरस्सतंनिक्षिप्यवानरम् ।सुग्रीवोऽऽभिमुखश्शत्रुंप्रतस्थेपादपायुधः","trans":"Sugriva, being a hero himself, uprooting a tree as a weapon, went towards the enemy after having assigned Sushena the responsibility of protection of Vanaras.","words":[{"d":"सःसुग्रीवः","m":"that Sugriva"},{"d":"आत्मनः","m":"himself"},{"d":"सदृशम्","m":"for the protection"},{"d":"वीरम्","m":"hero"},{"d":"तंवानरम्","m":"of the Vanaras"},{"d":"निक्षिप्य","m":"uprooting"},{"d":"पादपायुधः","m":"tree as weapon"},{"d":"शत्रुम्","m":"at the enemy"},{"d":"अभिमुख","m":"towards"}]},{"v":8,"dev":"पार्श्वतःपृष्ठतश्चास्यसर्वेयूथाधिपास्स्वयम् ।अनुजह्रुर्महाशैलान् विविधांश्चमहाद्रुमान्","trans":"All the leaders of the army themselves seizing hold of huge mountains and trees of several kinds followed his side.","words":[{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"स्वयम्","m":"themselves"},{"d":"अस्य","m":"their"},{"d":"पार्श्वतः","m":"side"},{"d":"पृष्ठतश्च","m":"seizing"},{"d":"महाशैलान्","m":"huge mountains"},{"d":"विविधान्","m":"many"},{"d":"वनस्पतींश्च","m":"also trees"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"सनदन्युधिसुग्रीवस्स्वरेणमहतामहान् ।पातयन्विविधांश्चान्यान्ञ्जगामोत्तमराक्षसान्","trans":"Great Sugriva roaring at high pitch in war destroyed several other Rakshasas and went towards the best of Rakshasas.","words":[{"d":"महान्","m":"great"},{"d":"सुग्रीवः","m":"Sugriva"},{"d":"युधि","m":"in war"},{"d":"महता","m":"huge"},{"d":"सनदन्","m":"roared"},{"d":"विविधान्","m":"several"},{"d":"अन्यान्","m":"others"},{"d":"पोथयन्","m":"destroying"},{"d":"उत्तमराक्षसान्","m":"best of Rakshasas"},{"d":"ममन्थ","m":"towards"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"ममन्थ च महाकायान्राक्षसान्वानरेश्वरः ।युगान्तसमयेवायुःप्रवृद्धानगमानिव","trans":"The Vanara Lord of gigantic body, moving like the wind, tortuously destroyed the Rakshasas like a huge wind destroying the universe.","words":[{"d":"महाकायः","m":"of gigantic body"},{"d":"युगास्तसमये","m":"at the end of the universe"},{"d":"प्रवृद्धान्","m":"huge"},{"d":"अगमानिव","m":"like the wind moving tortuously"},{"d":"राक्षसान्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"ममन्थच","m":"destroyed"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"राक्षसानामनीकेषुशैलवर्षंववर्ष ह ।अश्मवर्षंयथामेघःपक्षिसङ्घेषुकानने","trans":"Just as clouds shower hail stones on flocks of birds in the forest, Sugriva rained showers of rocks on the Rakshasas.","words":[{"d":"मेघः","m":"clouds"},{"d":"कानने","m":"in the forest"},{"d":"पक्षिसङ्घेषु","m":"flocks of birds"},{"d":"अश्मवर्षंयथा","m":"hail stones"},{"d":"राक्षसानाम्","m":"on Rakshasas"},{"d":"शैलवर्षम्","m":"shower of rocks"},{"d":"ववर्ष","m":"rained"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"कपिराजविमुक्तैस्तैश्शैलवर्षैस्तुराक्षसाः ।विकीर्णशिरसःपेतुर्निकृत्ताइवपर्वताः","trans":"Hit by the rocks rained by the Vanara king, the Rakshasas with heads broken and body mutilated had fallen like mountains.","words":[{"d":"राक्षसाः","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"कपिराजविमुक्तै:","m":"hit by Vanara king's rocks"},{"d":"तैः","m":"they"},{"d":"विकीर्णशिरसः","m":"broken heads"},{"d":"पर्वताः","m":"mountains"}]},{"v":13,"dev":"अथसंक्षीयमाणेषुराक्षसेषुसमन्ततः ।सुग्रीवेणप्रभग्नेषुपतत्सुनिनदत्सु च विरूपाक्षस्स्वकंनामधन्वीविश्राव्यराक्षसः ।रथादाप्लुत्यदुर्धर्षोगजस्कन्धमुपारुहत्","trans":"And thereafter, all the Rakshasas shattered by Sugriva, tormented, fallen on the ground were shouting. Seeing that Virupaksha, himself, who is difficult to encounter, holding his bow, announcing his name, jumped from the chariot onto an elephant in a rut.","words":[{"d":"अथ","m":"and thereafter"},{"d":"सुग्रीवेण","m":"by Sugriva"},{"d":"प्रभग्नेषु","m":"shattered"},{"d":"राक्षसेषु","m":"all the Rakshasas"},{"d":"संक्षीयमाणेषु","m":"tormented"},{"d":"निनदत्सु च","m":"shouting"},{"d":"धन्वी","m":"holding bow"},{"d":"राक्षसः","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"स्वम्","m":"himself"},{"d":"नाम","m":"name"},{"d":"विश्राव्य","m":"announcing"},{"d":"रथात्","m":"from chariot"},{"d":"आप्लुत्य","m":"jumped"},{"d":"गजस्कन्धम्","m":"on to an elephant in rut"},{"d":"उपारुहत्","m":"seated"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"अथसंक्षीयमाणेषुराक्षसेषुसमन्ततः ।सुग्रीवेणप्रभग्नेषुपतत्सुनिनदत्सु च विरूपाक्षस्स्वकंनामधन्वीविश्राव्यराक्षसः ।रथादाप्लुत्यदुर्धर्षोगजस्कन्धमुपारुहत्","trans":"And thereafter, all the Rakshasas shattered by Sugriva, tormented, fallen on the ground were shouting. Seeing that Virupaksha, himself, who is difficult to encounter, holding his bow, announcing his name, jumped from the chariot onto an elephant in a rut.","words":[{"d":"अथ","m":"and thereafter"},{"d":"सुग्रीवेण","m":"by Sugriva"},{"d":"प्रभग्नेषु","m":"shattered"},{"d":"राक्षसेषु","m":"all the Rakshasas"},{"d":"संक्षीयमाणेषु","m":"tormented"},{"d":"निनदत्सु च","m":"shouting"},{"d":"धन्वी","m":"holding bow"},{"d":"राक्षसः","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"स्वम्","m":"himself"},{"d":"नाम","m":"name"},{"d":"विश्राव्य","m":"announcing"},{"d":"रथात्","m":"from chariot"},{"d":"आप्लुत्य","m":"jumped"},{"d":"गजस्कन्धम्","m":"on to an elephant in rut"},{"d":"उपारुहत्","m":"seated"}]},{"v":15,"dev":"स तंद्विरदमारुह्यविरूपाक्षोमहारथः ।वनर्दभनीमनिर्ह्रादंवानरानभ्यधावत","trans":"That great charioteer Virupaksha ascended the elephant, frightening like a lion, and rushed towards Vanaras roaring.","words":[{"d":"महारथः","m":"great charioteer"},{"d":"सःविरूपाक्षः","m":"that Virupaksha"},{"d":"तंद्विरदमा","m":"elephant"},{"d":"आरुह्य","m":"ascending"},{"d":"अथ","m":"then"},{"d":"भीमनिर्ह्रादम्","m":"frightening like lion"},{"d":"ननर्द","m":"roared"},{"d":"वानरान्","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"अभ्यधावत","m":"rushed towards"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"सुग्रीवे स शरान्घोरान्विससर्जचमूमुखे ।स्थापयामासचोद्विग्नान्राक्षसान् सम्प्रहर्षयन्","trans":"Releasing arrows at the army of Vanaras and Sugriva, he (Virupaksha) pierced arrows and relieved the Rakshasas of fear and made them happy.","words":[{"d":"चमूमुखे","m":"at the army"},{"d":"सुग्रीवे","m":"at Sugriva"},{"d":"घोरान्","m":"dreadful"},{"d":"शरान्","m":"arrows"},{"d":"विससर्ज","m":"released"},{"d":"उद्विग्नान्","m":"pierced"},{"d":"राक्षसान्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"सम्प्रहर्षयन्","m":"made them happy"},{"d":"स्थापयामास","m":"relieving from fear"}]},{"v":17,"dev":"सतुविद्धश्शितैर्बाणैःकपीन्द्रस्तेनरक्षसा ।चुक्रोध स महाक्रोधोवधेचास्यमनोदधे","trans":"The king of Vanaras, pained by the shafts of Rakshasa, roared, and became very furious. He set in his mind to kill the Rakshasa.","words":[{"d":"तेन","m":"by that"},{"d":"रक्षसा","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"शितैः","m":"sharp"},{"d":"बाणैः","m":"shafts"},{"d":"सःकपीन्द्रः","m":"that king of Vanaras"},{"d":"चुक्रोश","m":"roared"},{"d":"महाक्रोधः","m":"very furious"},{"d":"अस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"वधे","m":"killing"},{"d":"मनः","m":"mind"},{"d":"दधे","m":"set in mind"}]},{"v":18,"dev":"ततःपादपमुद्धृत्यशूरस्सम्प्रधनोहरिः ।अभिपत्यजघानास्यप्रमुखेतुमहागजम्","trans":"Then springing up, the valiant Vanara uprooting a tree struck the face of the Rakshasa seated on the great elephant.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"सम्प्रधनः","m":"springing up"},{"d":"शूरः","m":"valiant"},{"d":"पादपम्","m":"trees"},{"d":"उद्धृत्य","m":"uprooting"},{"d":"अस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"तु","m":"also"},{"d":"महागजम्","m":"on the great elephant"},{"d":"अभिपत्य","m":"struck"},{"d":"प्रमुखे","m":"at face"},{"d":"जघान","m":"struck"}]},{"v":19,"dev":"स तुप्रहाराभिहतस्सुग्रीवेणमहागजः ।अपासर्पद्धनुर्मात्रंनिषसादननाद च","trans":"Overwhelmed by the blow of Sugriva, that great elephant retreated four cubits, distressed, and roared.","words":[{"d":"सुग्रीवेण","m":"by Sugriva"},{"d":"प्रहाराभिहतः","m":"overwhelmed with blow"},{"d":"सः","m":"that"},{"d":"महागजः","m":"great elephant"},{"d":"धनुर्मात्रम्","m":"distance of four cubits"},{"d":"पासर्पत्","m":"retreated"},{"d":"निषसाद","m":"distressed"},{"d":"ननाद च","m":"and roared"}]},{"v":20,"dev":"गजात्तुमथितात्तूर्णमपक्रम्य स वीर्यवान् ।राक्षसोऽऽभिमुखश्शत्रुंप्रत्युद्गम्यततःकपिम् आर्षभंचर्मखडगं च प्रगृह्यलघुविक्रमः ।भर्त्सयन्निवसुग्रीवमाससादव्यवस्थितम्","trans":"That valiant Rakshasa hero jumped down quickly from the wounded elephant, seizing hold of a shield made of bull's hide and a sword, advancing towards the enemy who stood firmly, and facing him, as if threatening him.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"सः","m":"that"},{"d":"वीर्यवान्","m":"valiant hero"},{"d":"राक्षसः","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"मथितात्","m":"wounded"},{"d":"गजात्","m":"elephant"},{"d":"तूर्णम्","m":"quickly"},{"d":"अपक्रम्य","m":"getting down"},{"d":"शत्रुम्","m":"the enemy"},{"d":"कपिम्","m":"monkey"},{"d":"आर्षभम्","m":"made of bull's"},{"d":"चर्म","m":"hide"},{"d":"खडगं च","m":"and sword"},{"d":"प्रगृह्य","m":"seizing"},{"d":"व्यवस्थितम्","m":"firmly seated"},{"d":"सुग्रीवम्","m":"Sugriva"},{"d":"भर्त्सयन्निव","m":"as if threatening"},{"d":"आससाद","m":"went towards"}]},{"v":21,"dev":"गजात्तुमथितात्तूर्णमपक्रम्य स वीर्यवान् ।राक्षसोऽऽभिम